								<node id="editorData">
									<children>
										<node id="data" key="key">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Fade up on the majesty of the outer planes. All is quiet, still, tranquil, then - something begins to happen. A new constellation begins to form in the shape of Gale's tattoo, tendrils of Netherese magic flickering around him like flashes of lightning. Pure, unbirdled power. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;A second symbol forms, of a similar size to Gale's. This one in the shape of Mystra's sigil, its magic the purer white/blue of the Weave. Then, we see Gale - in god-human or god-illithid form. He stands on the rippling firmament of the outer planes, Mystra before him." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
