											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Her piece said, Mystra disappears. The tattoo on Gale's chest begins to glow, his powers coming fully into being. He smiles to himself - godhood is his. In the Astral expanse above him, his symbol appears, glowing with power.  The God of Ambition has arrived." />
